# EchoFrame France Subrental — backend environment template.
#
# LOCAL USE:  copy this file to backend/.env and paste your keys.
#               cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
#             backend/.env is gitignored — it is never committed.
#
# PRODUCTION: do NOT use a file. Set these same keys in the Render
#             dashboard:  echoframe-france-api → Environment tab.
#
# Any key left blank/absent → that source falls back to seed data.
# The app runs fine with everything blank; keys only unlock live data.

# --- Airbnb comps ------------------------------------------------
# Apify scraper REMOVED 2026-05: the actor ignored its per-call item
# cap and Render's cache is ephemeral, so every request re-scraped
# whole cities (~$50 in one session). Comps are seed-only now — there
# is no key and no per-call cost. Do not re-introduce a paid scraper
# without an Apify-side hard budget AND a verified item cap.

# --- Primary STR benchmark (ADR / occupancy / RevPAR series) ------
# AirROI. ~$10/mo, $10 min top-up, covers 5/7 zones. Key:
#   https://www.airroi.com/api/developer/activate
AIRROI_API_KEY=

# --- Live French news headlines in the signals feed ---------------
# NewsData.io. Free tier: 200 req/day. Key:
#   https://newsdata.io/register
NEWSDATA_API_KEY=

# --- Narrative briefing language polish (optional) ----------------
# Anthropic. Deterministic draft is the always-on fallback.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Optional / not required (documented for completeness) --------
# INSEE Melodi: anon endpoint currently broken; key does not help yet.
INSEE_API_KEY=
# Banque de France WebStat: needs a key, currently uses fallback consts.
BDF_API_KEY=
